    <div class="flex w-full mb-20 flex-wrap">
      <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font text-gray-900 lg:w-1/3 lg:mb-0 mb-4">Meet Our Dedicated Team</h1>
      <p class="lg:pl-6 lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">
        At [Your Company Name], we take pride in our dedicated team of professionals who work tirelessly to deliver exceptional results. Our team is the backbone of our success, and their commitment to excellence is reflected in every project we undertake.
    
        Our gallery showcases the hardworking individuals behind the scenes. They are more than just employees; they are the heart and soul of our company. We believe in fostering a culture of collaboration, innovation, and growth, and our team embodies these values.
    
        As you explore our gallery, you'll get a glimpse of the passion, creativity, and expertise that drives us forward. We are more than just a company; we are a family working together to achieve greatness.
    
        Join us on this visual journey and discover the people who make [Your Company Name] the success it is today.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap md:-m-2 -m-1">
